{"id":2151,"date":"2024-11-22T16:19:55","date_gmt":"2024-11-22T16:19:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2151"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:13:02","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:13:02","slug":"ev-checker-changer","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/ev-checker-changer\/","title":{"rendered":"EV Checker &amp; Changer (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Battle Frontier<\/strong> &#8211; Behind a stall in the top-right corner of the area<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Maximizes or purges one of the select Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s EVs<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Battle Points<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>50 BP<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Start by flying to the Seaport City Pokemon Center and enter the connector to the north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-seaport-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Seaport City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Outside the gate connector, start following the path east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-walking-east-after-exiting-the-connector.jpg\" alt=\"Walking east after exiting the connector. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking east after exiting the connector.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue following the path north when you can\u2019t go east anymore.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-following-the-same-path-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the same path north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the same path north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The EV Changer is the Black Belt NPC behind the first stall you see.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-ev-changers-stall.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the EV Changer\u2019s stall. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the EV Changer\u2019s stall.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/05-pokemon-unbound-every-service-offered-by-the-ev-changer.jpg\" alt=\"Every service offered by the EV Changer. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Every service offered by the EV Changer.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The EV Changer offers three primary services:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Maximizing one Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s Effort Value in a stat for 50 Battle Points<\/li>\n<li>Purging a Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s Effort Value on a stat for 5 Battle Points<\/li>\n<li>Viewing the EVs and IVs of every Pokemon in your party<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2152,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-2151","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2151","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2143"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2152"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2151"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2151"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}